            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/step-6-1650382715602-x1500.jpg",
            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>While the fish is cooking, chop the<strong> parsley</strong> finely, including the stalks</p><p>Stir most of the <strong>chopped parsley</strong> (save the rest for garnish!) carefully through the cooked stew – this is your<strong> Mediterranean-style basa stew</strong></p>",
      "order": 7,
      "media": {
        "images": [
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/step-7-1650382725296-x200.jpg",
            "width": 200
